			"## VARIANS REGLER / VARIANCE RULES",
			"",
			"### Grundlæggende definition / Basic definition",
			"",
			"**Diskret variabel:**",
			"$$ \\text{Var}(X) = E[(X - E[X])^2] = \\sum_x (x - E[X])^2 \\cdot f_X(x) $$",
			"",
			"**Kontinuert variabel:**",
			"$$ \\text{Var}(X) = E[(X - E[X])^2] = \\int_{-\\infty}^{\\infty} (x - E[X])^2 \\cdot f_X(x) \\, dx $$",
			"",
			"**Alternativ formel (lettere at beregne):**",
			"$$ \\text{Var}(X) = E[X^2] - (E[X])^2 $$",
			"",
			"---",
			"",
			"### Lineær transformation / Linear transformation",
			"",
			"**Konstant addition (ingen effekt på varians):**",
			"$$ \\text{Var}(X + b) = \\text{Var}(X) $$",
			"",
			"**Multiplikation med konstant:**",
			"$$ \\text{Var}(aX) = a^2 \\text{Var}(X) $$",
			"",
			"**Generel lineær transformation:**",
