			"",
			"### Sum af variable / Sum of variables",
			"",
			"**To variable (generelt):**",
			"$$ \\text{Var}(X + Y) = \\text{Var}(X) + \\text{Var}(Y) + 2\\text{Cov}(X,Y) $$",
			"",
			"**To uafhængige variable:**",
			"$$ \\text{Var}(X + Y) = \\text{Var}(X) + \\text{Var}(Y) \\quad \\text{hvis } X \\perp Y $$",
			"",
			"**Differens af variable:**",
			"$$ \\text{Var}(X - Y) = \\text{Var}(X) + \\text{Var}(Y) - 2\\text{Cov}(X,Y) $$",
			"",
			"**Lineær kombination:**",
			"$$ \\text{Var}(aX + bY) = a^2\\text{Var}(X) + b^2\\text{Var}(Y) + 2ab\\text{Cov}(X,Y) $$",
			"",
			"**n uafhængige variable:**",
			"$$ \\text{Var}\\left(\\sum_{i=1}^n X_i\\right) = \\sum_{i=1}^n \\text{Var}(X_i) \\quad \\text{hvis alle } X_i \\perp X_j $$",
			"",
			"---",
			"",
			"### Standardafvigelse / Standard deviation",
